thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by JP

author: JP
title: JP
text: Picked up day late, not delivered in timeframe. Couldn't track online - link down. Was told by online assistant to phone through to track, couldn't track over phone - systems down. Chased again after non-delivery and was told it was self serve product and she couldn't track for me. Eventually found sitting in a depot for over a week.
